        "intro_text": "<p>At ZIENER, we love winter sports and exercise in the great outdoors. It is therefore only natural that we want to preserve this nature. In addition to our commitment at a local level in our home town of Oberammergau, we have been dedicated to ecological and social issues for several years by processing environmentally friendly materials, supporting climate protection projects and advocating fair working conditions. In detail, this means that ZIENER is using more and more recycled fabrics, renewable, natural materials and PFAS-free impregnations.<\/p>"
